rComments: The lectures are right out of the text book. The prof was pretty helpful during office hours but the midterm paper is hard.

Can be difficult to follow at times.  If you come to class, read the book you should do fine.  This prof is definitely not for people who expect easy marks. The challenge of doing good in his class is what makes it fun.

If you are in this class, get out while you still can!!!! An extremely uninspiring person. He undermines students' questions and contributions in class; his lectures are non-sequential; and he teaches a subjective subject in an objective way.

Terrible professor! Extremely patronizing when students ask questions, discusses marks publicly, and conveys his subject matter poorly. The marks for this class were so low and widely distributed that the head of the department contacted him and requested he try to increase them. I know as I called and asked how my mark went from a B to a B+
